data.description: Welcome home to this charming single-level haven on a sprawling 1.22 acre oasis. Embrace the peace of country living while savoring the convenience of town nearby. The ample outdoor space provides opportunities for gardening, recreational activities, or potential expansion. Interior features include: open concept living bathed in natural light, 2 bedrooms with attached bathrooms, newer carpet, & mud room. Exterior features include: Large manicured yard, dotted with mature trees, and new fruit trees, a large covered patio perfect for summer BBQ?s and starlit gatherings, 2 tool sheds, ample parking, and the tranquil Zell ditch and sound of the Walla Walla River. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or a place to create lasting memories, your fixer upper dreams can come true here!
